data.description: Great location! This home features a spacious living room with an open floor concept. 3 bedrooms plus a bonus room with 2 full bathrooms. Inside laundry space and an attached 1 car garage. New roof 2018. New paint and carpet. The back yard is spacious, featuring an above ground swimming pool with a wood deck surrounding the pool. Pool can be removed if you decide.
